title: BurnAware Professional v6.9.4-ADMIN@CRACK
description:
BurnAware Professional v6.9.4 with new ADMIN@CRACK (07 April 2014).

BurnAware Professional is a powerful, VERY LIGHT CD, DVD and BD disc burning solution intended for users who need maximum control over every aspect of the burning process and use multiple burners for mass-production of various discs and quick creation of disc-to-disc copies.

Install notes:

1. Install program.
2. Use patch.
3. Run License.reg file.
